data.englishTranslation: O Allah, there is no portent other than Your portent, no goodness other than Your goodness, and none worthy of worship other than You.
data.transliteration: Allaahumma laa tayra 'illaa tayruka, wa laa khayra 'illaa khayruka, wa laa 'ilaaha ghayruka.
data.arabicVerse: اللَّهُمَّ لَا طَيْرَ إِلَاَّ طَيْرُكَ، وَلَا خَيْرَ إِلَاَّ خَيْرُكَ، وَلَا إِلَهَ غَيْرُكَ
